<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idf662929d-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5" identifier="/us/usc/t46/s3310"><num value="3310">§ 3310.</num><heading> Records of certification</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall keep records of certificates of inspection of vessels and of all acts in the examination and inspection of vessels, whether of approval or disapproval.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idf662929e-2930-11f1-96a8-b9bd2a0a99b5">(<ref href="/us/pl/98/89">Pub. L. 98–89</ref>, <date date="1983-08-26">Aug. 26, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/97/515">97 Stat. 515</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
